Class DeleteFinalMessageProcessor

  • java.lang.Object

    @Qualifier(value="deleteFinalMessageProcessor")
public class DeleteFinalMessageProcessor
extends AbstractFinalMessageProcessor
    FinalMessageProcessor implementation that does delete given message from datastore. It does delete message and all related entities as well.
    Since:
    2.1
    Author:
    Karel Kovarik
